		<strong>2. copilot-agent-lite</strong> — A lightweight GitHub Copilot subscription agent
		runtime, keeping Copilot features available outside official client boundaries.<br />
		<strong>3. Kijiji Real-Time Monitor</strong> — A wheel-price monitoring bot for Kijiji
